        createBrowserWebDriver() - Main class that creates the selenium web drivers, This is wrapper method that allows you to pass in a string for the platform.

        Parameters:
        remote - - Local, proxy,saucelabs must use
        browserVersion - = browser version only used when connecting to saucelabs
        platform - - windows,Linux,Mac. Used when connecting to proxy, or browser stack, or saucelabs
        osVersion - - Windows (7,8,8.1,10), MAC(OS_X), Linux not used leave blank
        browser - - (Firefox,Chrome,IOS,Android,IE)
        setupString - - Test description
        Returns:
        RemoteWebDriver - create a webdriver based on the inputs
        See Also:
        - webdriver created based on input
